amin A, Potassium Iodide, Acetylcysteine, Nandrolone, Golimumab, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, More', 'Rifamycin, Paromomycin, Rifaximin, Chlorhexidine, Povidone-iodine, Tetracycline, Mupirocin, Rifamycin, Oxytetracycline, Demeclocycline, Rifaximin, More', 1767369485);
