ly avoid the use of products containing ginkgo biloba.', 'Synergism', 'Patients should consult a healthcare provider before taking any herbal or alternative medicine.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/143456/', '', 'Memantine, Aducanumab', 'Ambenonium, Pilocarpine, Cevimeline, Pyridostigmine, Latanoprost, Apraclonidine, Methazolamide, Pilocarpine, Clonidine, Acetylcholine, Betaxolol, More', 1767369485);
